{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-tutorial-js","path":"/zh/tutorial/Visualization/BrowseMap/MapNavigation/","webpackCompilationHash":"b56fc1f276773fcd7503","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h3 id=\"使用说明\"><a href=\"#%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><img src=\"/read-56e09d9020b6fe36d2da63ae2fd275c5.gif\">使用说明</h3>\n<p>地图窗口的右侧区域为地图窗口的导航条，可用来对地图进行浏览控制，包括对当前地图进行放大、缩小、平移等操作。</p>\n<h3 id=\"操作步骤\"><a href=\"#%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E6%AD%A5%E9%AA%A4\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><img src=\"/read-56e09d9020b6fe36d2da63ae2fd275c5.gif\">操作步骤</h3>\n<p>在窗口中打开地图，单击“ <strong>地图</strong> ”选项卡“ <strong>浏览</strong> ”组的“ <strong>设置</strong> ”按钮，在“设置”的下拉选项中，点击“ <strong>显示导航条</strong>\n”按钮，地图窗口右侧会显示导航条。</p>\n<p>导航条包括位于上方的圆盘和位于下方的滑块两部分。其中，圆盘控制地图的平移方式，包括向上平移、向下平移、向左平移和向右平移四种；滑块控制地图的分辨率大小，拖动滑块即可实现地图的放大与缩小操作。</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"地图导航","next":null,"prev":null},"fields":{"path":"content\\tutorial\\Visualization\\BrowseMap\\MapNavigation.zh.md","slug":"/zh/tutorial/Visualization/BrowseMap/MapNavigation/","langKey":"zh"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/zh/tutorial/Visualization/BrowseMap/MapNavigation/"}}}